Package: vortex-kernel
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: i486
Maintainer: Vortex86 A9100 Project
Description: Linux 5.10 LTS kernel and modules for Vortex86 A9100
 Provides the bzImage kernel and loadable kernel modules
 built for i486 with FPU emulation and CMPXCHG8B support.
Section: kernel
Priority: required
Source: https://github.com/vincenzosco/Vortex-A9100-Linux-Image
